overview.en: The HAOMO project, by integrating blockchain technology with an innovative economic model, not only revolutionizes the field of health supplement effect tracking and precise medication but also provides higher trust and efficiency for relevant stakeholders. As the project progresses, we believe that HAOMO willbecome an important force in the global healthcare sector.
overview.zh: HAOMO 项目结合了区块链技术和创新的经济模型，不仅为保健品效果跟踪和精准用药领域带来革命性变革，也为相关利益方提供更高的信任和效率。随着项目的推进，我们相信 HAOMO 将成为全球健康保健领域的重要力量。
